g.data-name: Pueblo Unido provides legal service navigation client advocacy
g.text: Pueblo Unido provides legal service navigation, client advocacy,
and financial assistance to immigrants who are detained at the NW
Detention Center in Tacoma, WA, or who are in removal proceedings
at the Portland Immigration Court. We do not charge for our support
services. Since 2017, Pueblo Unido has provided
over 225 free legal consultations, paid towards 35 attorney retainer
fees, connected over 90 people to free legal aid, and helped
22 people get released from detention. 7 people supported by
